{"tid":2422467,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"穗珍再遭同學爆大鑊：取笑徐信愛醜樣兼屈對方吸煙","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T15:31:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2455a4ec68ee7c1c6f3550d27f242ab0a0d08c","tid":2422467,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rVC5tYggEt8NzIBsoza12j6XU-Y=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESOU6B6FU5F4TMFN4VWR525RY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrVC5tYggEt8NzIBsoza12j6XU-Y%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESOU6B6FU5F4TMFN4VWR525RY4.jpg&h=ad0cf736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國演藝圈今個月接連爆出藝人涉校園暴力事件，牽涉的人物多不勝數，當中包括人氣劇《驅魔麵館》上位男星趙炳圭、「馬舞女」泫雅、女團(G)I-DLE的22歲成員穗珍、《梨泰院Class》金東希、男團Seventeen的23歲成員珉奎、韓片《勁舞Dancing癲》26歲女星朴慧秀等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：ITZY Lia涉校園暴力 朴慧秀方面懷疑網民為錢集體爆料<br />\n事務所否認霸凌<br />\n而女團(G)I-DLE的22歲成員穗珍早前被網民A某指控霸凌同學，事後穗珍所屬事務所CUBE承認穗珍曾與自稱受害人的同學吵架，但否認霸凌。及後穗珍遭網民要求退團，而童星出身的徐信愛與穗珍屬中學同學，當穗珍霸凌事件爆出時，她曾在社交網留言：「沒有解釋的餘地。」似暗示曾遭到穗珍的欺凌。雖然穗珍否認有欺凌徐信愛，但今日韓網卻出現題為《關於徐信愛》的文章，自稱是徐信愛和穗珍的中學同學就爆料指徐信愛讀書時曾長時期受到穗珍的欺負。<br />\n<br />\n學校老師早知情<br />\n網民表示：「班主任、學生主任老師、同班同學都知道（校園暴力事實）。」由於童星出道的徐信愛讀中學時已出演過不少作品，所以在學校亦為人認識，這令穗珍十分妒忌，經常聯同友人一起欺凌徐信愛。網民指：「她們會把香煙放到徐信愛的桌子內，然後向老師舉報，之後就傳出徐信愛吸煙傳聞，其父母要到學校道歉。」同時穗珍亦不時攻擊徐信愛的樣貌，指她長得這樣醜也能當藝人，反問她是否覺得丟人。<br />\n<br />\n典禮後傷心流淚<br />\n網民繼續大爆表示穗珍曾試過偷走徐信愛父母的感謝信，令到徐信愛在畢業典禮後傷心流淚。而網民指徐信愛性格樂觀，雖然受到欺凌但仍然忠實地度過學校生活，又表示：「她經常主動跟周圍的人打招呼，給我們買東西，謝謝我們陪她一起走。對在這種地獄中堅持並茁壯成長的人來說，反指她是加害者，這是話嗎？所以我要站出來講出真相。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hQ-wfJlQMObvFZxnfP25D4_ZOmU=/802x520/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NQJ6LUUNMZGRFLEDZ7ABINMWP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhQ-wfJlQMObvFZxnfP25D4_ZOmU%3D%2F802x520%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNQJ6LUUNMZGRFLEDZ7ABINMWP4.jpg&h=5c8dde54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-jAEf3zVCyUb-xQf-k7-2c8MB00=/802x1062/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JQEP7YRKBNDIVHH7HZTD2Y47DU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-jAEf3zVCyUb-xQf-k7-2c8MB00%3D%2F802x1062%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJQEP7YRKBNDIVHH7HZTD2Y47DU.jpg&h=d58d7f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210225/USE5456V2JETVLW6S44NB2F3R4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210225%2FUSE5456V2JETVLW6S44NB2F3R4%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFSpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=3e35aa41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210225%2FUSE5456V2JETVLW6S44NB2F3R4%2F&h=312e0320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210225/USE5456V2JETVLW6S44NB2F3R4/</a>"},{"pid":"e21a38473a00079ca2ae4915cd8792a2adf51251","tid":2422467,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"我爆導狗大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a4194cabbf7a475e61e0f9a9585e9b45e8f13a","tid":2422467,"uid":229026,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"笑人醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad6136efde453b698f2eb0b40717b221cdeda9","tid":2422467,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a4194cabbf7a475e61e0f9a9585e9b45e